  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This pilot study aims to assess a new device designed for an objective measure of sleep
      parameters. The purpose of the device is to assess, in a more simple and precise way, the
      impact of deep brain stimulation on patient's sleep.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
